{"title":"二分搜尋（二分答案/最小化最大值/最大化最小值/第K小）","src":"https://leetcode.cn/circle/discuss/SqopEo/","last_update":"2026-02-24T14:23:02.465505+00:00","summary":"![二分題單](https://pic.leetcode.cn/1711713491-SoiQWc-t2.png)\n\n> 圖：閉區間二分迴圈結束時的左右指標位置（查詢第一個 8）\n\n**刷題建議**：初學者建議先刷難度 < 1700 分的題目，進階題目常結合資料結構、圖論等\n\n**本題單涵蓋**：\n- 基礎二分查詢（查詢元素、統計個數）\n- 二分答案（最小化最大值、最大化最小值、第 K 小）\n- 三分法與其他應用\n\n**C++ 模板**：\n\n```cpp\n// 閉區間 [left, right] 二分模板\nint search(vector<int>& nums, int target) {\n    int left = 0, right = nums.size() - 1; // 搜尋範圍 [left, right]\n    while (left <= right) {\n        int mid = left + (right - left) / 2; // 防溢位寫法\n        if (nums[mid] == target) {\n            return mid;\n        } else if (nums[mid] < target) {\n            left = mid + 1;\n        } else {\n            right = mid - 1;\n        }\n    }\n    return -1;\n}\n```","children":[{"title":"1. 基礎","src":null,"problems":[{"id":"34","title":"在排序陣列中查詢元素的第一個和最後一個位置","slug":"find-first-and-last-position-of-element-in-sorted-array","src":"https://leetcode.cn/problems/find-first-and-last-position-of-element-in-sorted-array/","solution":null,"score":null,"isPremium":false},{"id":"35","title":"搜尋插入位置","slug":"search-insert-position","src":"https://leetcode.cn/problems/search-insert-position/","solution":null,"score":null,"isPremium":false},{"id":"704","title":"二分查詢","slug":"binary-search","src":"https://leetcode.cn/problems/binary-search/","solution":null,"score":null,"isPremium":false},{"id":"744","title":"尋找比目標字母大的最小字母","slug":"find-smallest-letter-greater-than-target","src":"https://leetcode.cn/problems/find-smallest-letter-greater-than-target/","solution":null,"score":null,"isPremium":false},{"id":"2529","title":"正整數和負整數的最大計數","slug":"maximum-count-of-positive-integer-and-negative-integer","src":"https://leetcode.cn/problems/maximum-count-of-positive-integer-and-negative-integer/","solution":null,"score":null,"isPremium":false}],"children":[],"isLeaf":true,"summary":"講解：[二分查找 紅藍染色法【基礎算法精講 04】](/link/?target=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bilibili.com%2Fvideo%2FBV1AP41137w7%2F)\n\n設 nums 為遞增（非遞減）陣列，長為 n。\n\n| **需求** | **寫法** | **如果不存在** |\n| --- | --- | --- |\n| $\\geq x$ 的第一個元素的下標 | lowerBound(nums,x) | 結果為 n |\n| $>x$ 的第一個元素的下標 | lowerBound(nums,x+1) | 結果為 n |\n| $<x$ 的最後一個元素的下標 | lowerBound(nums,x)−1 | 結果為 −1 |\n| $\\leq x$ 的最後一個元素的下標 | lowerBound(nums,x+1)−1 | 結果為 −1 |\n\n| **需求** | **寫法** |\n| --- | --- |\n| $<x$ 的元素個數 | lowerBound(nums,x) |\n| $\\leq x$ 的元素個數 | lowerBound(nums,x+1) |\n| $\\geq x$ 的元素個數 | n−lowerBound(nums,x) |\n| $>x$ 的元素個數 | n−lowerBound(nums,x+1) |\n\n注意 $<x$ 和 $\\geq x$ 互為補集，二者之和為 $n$。$\\leq x$ 和 $>x$ 同理。\n\n---\n\n![二分題單 二分查找 二分算法 二分入門 二分題目 力扣二分 leetcode 二分](https://pic.leetcode.cn/1711713491-SoiQWc-t2.png)\n\n> 圖：閉區間二分循環結束時的左右指標位置（查找第一個 8）\n\n**刷題建議**：初次刷題可以只刷難度低於 1700 分的題目。難度更高的題目常常結合其他算法（數據結構、圖論等），等學會其他算法再來刷本題單。\n\n---\n\n\n\n**二分搜尋核心**：\n- 適用於單調函式或有序序列\n- 每次將搜尋區間減半，時間複雜度 $O(\\log n)$"},{"title":"2. 進階","src":null,"problems":[{"id":"658","title":"找到 K 個最接近的元素","slug":"find-k-closest-elements","src":"https://leetcode.cn/problems/find-k-closest-elements/","solution":null,"score":null,"isPremium":false},{"id":"LCP 08","title":"劇情觸發時間","slug":"ju-qing-hong-fa-shi-jian","src":"https://leetcode.cn/problems/ju-qing-hong-fa-shi-jian/","solution":null,"score":null,"isPremium":false},{"id":"2819","title":"購買巧克力後的最小相對損失","slug":"minimum-relative-loss-after-buying-chocolates","src":"https://leetcode.cn/problems/minimum-relative-loss-after-buying-chocolates/","solution":null,"score":null,"isPremium":true},{"id":"1385","title":"兩個陣列間的距離值","slug":"find-the-distance-value-between-two-arrays","src":"https://leetcode.cn/problems/find-the-distance-value-between-two-arrays/","solution":null,"score":null,"isPremium":false},{"id":"2389","title":"和有限的最長子序列","slug":"longest-subsequence-with-limited-sum","src":"https://leetcode.cn/problems/longest-subsequence-with-limited-sum/","solution":null,"score":null,"isPremium":false},{"id":"1170","title":"比較字串最小字母出現頻次","slug":"compare-string