ull,"isPremium":false},{"id":"911","title":"線上選舉","slug":"online-election","src":"https://leetcode.cn/problems/online-election/","solution":null,"score":null,"isPremium":false}],"children":[{"title":"2.1 進階 > 思維擴展","src":null,"problems":[{"id":"1287","title":"有序陣列中出現次數超過 25% 的元素","slug":"element-appearing-more-than-25-in-sorted-array","src":"https://leetcode.cn/problems/element-appearing-more-than-25-in-sorted-array/","solution":null,"score":null,"isPremium":false},{"id":"1150","title":"檢查一個數是否在陣列中佔絕大多數","slug":"check-if-a-number-is-majority-element-in-a-sorted-array","src":"https://leetcode.cn/problems/check-if-a-number-is-majority-element-in-a-sorted-array/","solution":null,"score":null,"isPremium":true},{"id":"2476","title":"二叉搜索樹最近節點查詢","slug":"closest-nodes-queries-in-a-binary-search-tree","src":"https://leetcode.cn/problems/closest-nodes-queries-in-a-binary-search-tree/","solution":null,"score":null,"isPremium":false}],"children":[],"isLeaf":true}],"isLeaf":true,"summary":"\n\n**進階二分查詢技巧**：\n- 利用二分查詢解決「查詢滿足條件的最近元素」問題\n- 結合排序與雙指標，處理區間距離、頻次統計等\n- 適用於有序序列中的比較與計數操作\n\n```cpp\n// 查詢第一個 >= target 的位置（lowerBound）\nint lowerBound(vector<int>& nums, int target) {\n    int lo = 0, hi = nums.size(); // 左閉右開 [lo, hi)\n    while (lo < hi) {\n        int mid = lo + (hi - lo) / 2;\n        if (nums[mid] < target) {\n            lo = mid + 1;\n        } else {\n            hi = mid;\n        }\n    }\n    return lo;\n}\n```"},{"title":"3. 求最小","src":null,"problems":[{"id":"475","title":"供暖器","slug":"heaters","src":"https://leetcode.cn/problems/heaters/","solution":null,"score":null,"isPremium":false},{"id":"3807","title":"修復邊以遍歷圖的最小成本","slug":"minimum-cost-to-repair-edges-to-traverse-a-graph","src":"https://leetcode.cn/problems/minimum-cost-to-repair-edges-to-traverse-a-graph/","solution":null,"score":null,"isPremium":true},{"id":"2604","title":"喫掉所有穀子的最短時間","slug":"minimum-time-to-eat-all-grains","src":"https://leetcode.cn/problems/minimum-time-to-eat-all-grains/","solution"