blems/minimum-number-of-days-to-make-m-bouquets/","solution":null,"score":null,"isPremium":false},{"id":"3048","title":"標記所有下標的最早秒數 I","slug":"earliest-second-to-mark-indices-i","src":"https://leetcode.cn/problems/earliest-second-to-mark-indices-i/","solution":null,"score":null,"isPremium":false}],"children":[{"title":"3.1 求最小 > 思維擴展","src":null,"problems":[{"id":"1870","title":"準時到達的列車最小時速","slug":"minimum-speed-to-arrive-on-time","src":"https://leetcode.cn/problems/minimum-speed-to-arrive-on-time/","solution":null,"score":null,"isPremium":false},{"id":"3453","title":"分割正方形 I","slug":"separate-squares-i","src":"https://leetcode.cn/problems/separate-squares-i/","solution":null,"score":null,"isPremium":false}],"children":[],"isLeaf":true}],"isLeaf":true,"summary":"> “花費一個 log 的時間，增加了一個條件。” —— 二分答案\n\n---\n\n\n\n**核心思路**：\n- 尋找滿足條件的第一個位置\n- 當 `check(mid)` 為真時，答案在左側或當前位置，`high = mid - 1`, `ans = mid`\n\n```cpp\n// 二分答案求最小值：check(mid) 為 true 時收縮右邊界\nwhile (low <= high) {\n    int mid = low + (high - low) / 2;\n    if (check(mid)) { // 滿足條件，嘗試更小的答案\n        ans = mid;\n        high = mid - 1;\n    } else {\n        low = mid + 1;\n    }\n}\n```"},{"title":"4. 求最大","src":null,"problems":[{"id":"275","title":"H 指數 II","slug":"h-index-ii","src":"https://leetcode.cn/problems/h-index-ii/","solution":null,"score":null,"isPremium":false},{"id":"LCP 78","title":"城牆防線","slug":"Nsibyl","src":"https://leetcode.cn/problems/Nsibyl/","solution":null,"score":null,"isPremium":false},{"id":"1618","title":"找出適應螢幕的最大字號","slug":"maximum-font-to-fit-a-sentence-in-a-screen","src":"https://leetcode.cn/problems/maximum-font-to-fit-a-sentence-in-a-screen/","solution":null,"score":null,"isPremium":true},{"id":"1891","title":"割繩子","slug":"cutting-ribbons","src":"https://leetcode.cn/problems/cutting-ribbons/","solution":null,"score":null,"isPremium":true},{"id":"2137","title":"透過倒水操作讓所有的水桶所含水量相等","slug":"pour-water-between-buckets-to-make-water-levels-equal","src":"https://leetcode.cn/problems/pour